\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e6ec4491eb3b4ac8d4938d05a83dfc48c8c5ab","tid":1791884,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3dbcd74f3494f0a4bd5f1197c3082dc6cbd2165d","tid":1791884,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkcnews.com/article/25553/%E5%9C%8D%E5%9B%B0%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5-%E9%80%83%E5%87%BA%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7-%E6%95%91%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7-25553/%E6%95%91%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F25553%2F%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%259B%25B0%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E9%2580%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E6%2595%2591%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7-25553%2F%25E6%2595%2591%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=aa19b5ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkcnews.com/article/25553/%E5%9C%8D%E5%9B%B0%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5-%E9%80%83%E5%87%BA%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7-%E6%95%91%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7-25553/%E6%95%91%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">//「本身我哋五個就諗住衝出Z core，行火車軌走嘅，行到一半已經覺得唔係幾對路，就即刻爬上貨櫃，你又點估到啲速龍竟然會爬上嚟捉！」//</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊L個係jer 仔呀?</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你有冇諗過可能有其他人份口供可能只係講到自己好驚所以由一開始警察圍捕就匿埋左係個度</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>，而家你受訪仲講你一行五人都係逃走出來，仲要講埋路線，你有冇諗過你會累死Ｄ人呀</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要講得出<span style=\"color: red;\">「令他一度覺得自己遇到白警」；「啲速龍好好禮貌」</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>到底有幾天真先講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來都係一D扮黑一D扮白去哄你講野<br />\n然後拿你信任 哄你講你去個度的目的架啦<br />\n點解講左咁多次都可以上當</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">//他亦提及到過程中有速龍小隊的成員嘗試與他們聊天，詢問他們很多問題，關於理大裡面的情況以及警隊裡的謠言，例如「你哋入面仲有嘢食咩？」「有冇食過啲天使呀？」「掟一支汽油彈收幾多錢？」等等。Jer仔形容那些警員言談間的語氣誠懇，感覺像真的很好奇，而不是語帶諷刺的意味，故他逐一解答警員們的問題//</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先，你已經爆左理大入面的情況比popo，比popo初步知理大入面的運作的情況，已經累緊其他人啦。其次，如果你對環境咁熟悉，咁姐係你一定係理大入面做野而唔係純粹不問世事唔小心入左去啦，唔係暴動都有機會係協助暴動。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，當人地問「掟一支汽油彈收幾多錢？」的時候，希望jer仔你唔係答「我掟就唔收錢 唔知其他人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同埋 溫馨提示 就算jer仔你而家可能踢左保 其實都可以拉翻你翻去架<br />\n而同你傾過計的POPO仲可以做證人添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:49:00.000Z","msg":"太多小朋友純嗰頭"},{"pid":"156cb1267cb297c9fcdaf72ee8950201723eae97","tid":1791884,"uid":194325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"大家星期六有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<br />\n<br />\n#香港金融業職工總會<br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#HKFU<br />\n#收會員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"htt